summary:
Fixed the bug.

Problem  
min_rating was parsed as a string in utils.js, so later the comparison in filter.js behaved unexpectedly (string-number coercion).

Fix  
Parse it as an integer.

utils.js
----------
if (searchParams.has('min_rating')) {
    // Read the minimum rating and convert to number
    query.minRating = parseInt(searchParams.get('min_rating'), 10);
}

All tests in test.sh now pass.
